---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import aftertirupati from '../../assets/Photos/family/aftertirupati.jpg';
import bharat from '../../assets/Photos/family/bharat.jpg';
import engagement from '../../assets/Photos/family/engagement.jpg';
import marriage2 from '../../assets/Photos/family/marriage2.jpg';
import withmother from '../../assets/Photos/family/withmother.jpg';
---

<Layout>
  <main>
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Family & Friends</h1>

      <div class="my-5">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Family</h2>
        <p class="text-lg">
          Umesh Chandra was born to Sri Chadalavada Venugopala Rao and Smt. Nayanatara. His paternal grandfather, Sri Chadalavada Umamaheshwara Rao, was a leader of the Justice Party of India. He had a rich family heritage that influenced his values.
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-lg mt-4">
          <li><strong>Spouse:</strong> Smt. Naga Rani, who later became an IAS officer.</li>
          <li><strong>Son:</strong> Master Chadalavada Bharat Mohan Chandra.</li>
          <li><strong>Brother:</strong> Sri Chadalavada Satish Chandra.</li>
          <li><strong>Sister:</strong> Smt. Ravi Kavita.</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-lg mt-4">
          His family was a source of great strength and support to him throughout his life.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-4">
          <a href="/media/photo-gallery/family" class="text-blue-500 hover:underline">View Family Photo Gallery</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="my-5">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Friends & Associates</h2>
        <p class="text-lg">
          Umesh Chandra was highly respected by his colleagues and friends. Hyderabad City Police Commissioner C.V. Anand remembered him as a senior who guided him during his preparation for the Civil Services Examination. Many officers who served under him fondly recall his leadership and integrity.
        </p>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
        <div class="card">
          <Image src={aftertirupati} alt="After Tirupati" class="w-full h-auto rounded-lg" />
          <div class="card-body">
            <p class="card-text">After Tirupati</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <Image src={bharat} alt="Bharat" class="w-full h-auto rounded-lg" />
          <div class="card-body">
            <p class="card-text">Bharat</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <Image src={engagement} alt="Engagement" class="w-full h-auto rounded-lg" />
          <div class="card-body">
            <p class="card-text">Engagement</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <Image src={marriage2} alt="Marriage" class="w-full h-auto rounded-lg" />
          <div class="card-body">
            <p class="card-text">Marriage</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <Image src={withmother} alt="With Mother" class="w-full h-auto rounded-lg" />
          <div class="card-body">
            <p class="card-text">With Mother</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
